Package ch.supertomcat.bh.queue

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICalculateRateTimer  
    IDownloadListener
    Interface of QueueData for downloads, so they will know, when they are allowed to start the download, after they requested a download-slot.
    IDownloadQueueManagerListener
    Interface of QueueData to let listeners know when downloads-slots where changed or the count of downloaded files or bytes has changed.
    QueueManagerListener  
  • Class Summary

    DownloadQueueManager
    This class manages the download-slots.
    QueueManager

    Restriction
    This class is to set a limit of simultanious downloads for a domain.
